long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
** Work In Progress **
This extension provides a peek into your browsing patterns, to help you stay in control of your browsing habits.

Get a quick Tab Summary:
- Total number of links visited
- Interaction detailed
- Tab age 
- Page age vs  Idle Time


All tracking is done locally and nothing leaves your machine :)
Code available here:  https://github.com/Mimieam/TimeTab
